## Simulation and Report
Run full simulation and capture a .vcd waveform for a test vector.

Summarize results in sims/report.md, e.g.

| Test Case   | A  | B  | Sel | Output | Carry | Pass/Fail |
| ----------- | -- | -- | --- | ------ | ----- | --------- |
| Addition    | 10 | 5  | 000 | 15     | 0     | ✔️        |
| Subtraction | 5  | 10 | 001 | 251    | 1     | ✔️        |
| AND         | 12 | 10 | 010 | 8      | 0     | ✔️        |
| …           | …  | …  | …   | …      | …     | …         |
